snippet.title: DemonsAreCrazy Trailer [HD]
snippet.description:
Welcome to the underworld's first official election! Do you have what it take to be the next ruler of hell? Meet the epic action adventure MOBA of your (after) life time.

Choose from 18 starter demons (FPS, Hack&Slash, or MMO) and customize over a hundred of skills, a thousand of equipments. Hunt boss for special epic rewards. Go to open area and hang out with your fellow demons. The possibilities are endless in the underworld. Come and claim your Satan throne today!

Official Website: www.demonsarecrazy.com
FB: https://www.facebook.com/DemonsAreCrazy
Wiki: https://demonsarecrazy.gamepedia.com/DemonsAreCrazy_Wiki
